{"tid":538793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英報告指本港學術自由受威脅 教育局駁斥「無事實根據」","createTime":"2018-01-24T03:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T03:19:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3274c9b8893edc9b39e2ea2971d72b93317e1fb8","tid":538793,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180123/large/1516717903_c6b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180123%2Flarge%2F1516717903_c6b1.png&h=6525ec01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國組織「香港觀察」（Hong Kong Watch）發表學術自由報告，批評自雨傘運動後，本港學術自由受到威脅，包括大學校園被政治化，多名具爭議性的學者相繼面臨解僱或升遷受阻。教育局晚上回應評報告是「對香港高等教育作出一些無事實根據及公平的評論」，對此表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人重申，學術自由是香港一直推崇的社會價值，並受《基本法》保障，是香港高等教育賴以成功的基石，港府亦一直致力維護學術自由和院校自由。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指出，本港獲教資會資助的8間大學均是獨立自主的法定機構，各自有條例及規程，法例亦訂明各校所享的權力和自由。至於備受爭議的特首擔任各大學校監的「校監必然制」，發言人就稱是為了藉以維持政府與大學之間的連繫，亦是顯示當局對高等教育的支持，校監一職的權力及職務亦有相關條例和規程限制，強調有關制度一直行之有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180123/57746049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180123%2F57746049&d=8V3KJs1r2MXkCAdtcbJ4fGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=de1d829c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180123%2F57746049&h=cc019d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180123/57746049</a>"},{"pid":"56f09a1606235d88b5d9d890becf6a4bd676e4d0","tid":538793,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b05f634c1c2e0f4ee395bee3e61e84114bc5800f","tid":538793,"uid":146646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56f09a1606235d88b5d9d890becf6a4bd676e4d0","tid":538793,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,